title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4026.16 - Stable name-restriction on individual
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4026.16 - Stable name-restriction on individual

State Regulations

An individual cannot have registered more than one
stable name at the same time and, so long as such individual has a stable name
registered, he or she shall not use or permit the use of his of her real name
to identify his or her ownership interest in the racing qualities of any
horse. Notes
